{"tid":350420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"失蹤港商返港再走失","createTime":"2017-08-07T08:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T08:32:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50a9e04bbeea708f027050a074c8620e580bf789","tid":350420,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:30:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20114171&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20114171%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170807&d=7%2FtOmr58GaXyuYwrXBw2xW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=df67e293\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20114171%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170807&h=8ed98078\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20114171&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170807</a><br />\n<br />\n失蹤港商返港再走失<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】在東莞露宿街頭11年的港商陳志健（68歲，圖），經內地義工協助下，上周四返港與家人團聚，翌日他又在北區醫院走失，至昨凌晨巡警在上水古洞尋回，將其送返北區醫院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170807/large/a0206a.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170807%2Flarge%2Fa0206a.gif&d=7%2FtOmr58GaXyuYwrXBw2xW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=a6785172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170807/large/a0206a.gif</a> <img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170807/large/a0206a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170807%2Flarge%2Fa0206a.gif&h=d4c0c3be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n流連古洞兩日尋回<br />\n<br />\n陳志健上周四返港，被送往北區醫院留醫及觀察健康情況，並有兩社工跟進。翌日凌晨，醫院發現他失去蹤影，於是通知警方。昨凌晨1時許，途人發現一名老翁在古洞徘徊，覺得可疑報警。<br />\n警方接報趕抵，在河上鄉路一個巴士站發現該老翁蹤影。據悉，當時陳志健並無身份證明文件，而且難以溝通，但警方根據他身上寫有身份證號碼的紙張，確認他就是走失的陳志健，最終送返北區醫院，院方安排保安貼身監視。<br />\n消息稱，陳志健回港後，警方一直未能聯絡其家人，亦到過陳曾居住的灣仔住所拍門，惜無人應門。消息又稱，陳曾改名為陳達汶沿用至今，2006年3月11日離奇失蹤，家人報稱失蹤時名字為陳達汶，當陳今年年初在東莞被尋回時，義工得悉他叫陳志健，中港兩地警方其後核實身份證號碼及指紋，才證實他就是失蹤人士陳達汶。<br />\n■記者張家豪"},{"pid":"fb0ae7d18d70ff7f59c1def5f038089a1aca9bf4","tid":350420,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:32:08.000Z","msg":"之前係電話同佢視像對話個d屋企人呢 ?"}]}